title: More than 53,000 Beijing couples opt for second child (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) More than 53, 000 couples in Beijing have applied for a second child since the city changed its birth control policy in early 2014. By the end of September, 53,034 couples in Beijing had submitted
